00:09:36,173 --> 00:09:38,106
Machadinha.

157
00:09:38,106 --> 00:09:39,407
Fala sério!
Sam!

158
00:09:39,407 --> 00:09:41,109
Olha só.
É o David Yaeger.

159
00:09:41,109 --> 00:09:42,582
É.

160
00:09:42,582 --> 00:09:44,632
Aperte o botão.

161
00:09:49,786 --> 00:09:51,786
<i>Hora de picar e fatiar.</i>

162
00:09:51,786 --> 00:09:54,022
